00:17.520 --> 00:19.950
No one cares what <i>I</i> did?

00:20.080 --> 00:23.280
Wait, you fought, too, Old Man Shinpachi?

00:23.280 --> 00:27.290
Yes. If not for the battle that night,

00:27.560 --> 00:33.260
I might not be living 
as a samurai should now.

00:33.790 --> 00:35.240
Sounds awesome.

00:35.240 --> 00:37.510
I can't wait to hear 
what happens next, Sensei!

